      <p>Unlike regular antivirus tools, our app tracks hidden processes, suspicious file changes, and system setting modifications, even on rooted devices.</p>
      
      <h2>3. Message & App Activity Logging</h2>
      <p>You can keep a secure log of sent/deleted messages, app usage history, and installation attempts — essential for both personal security and forensic investigations.</p>
      
      <h2>4. Cloud-Synced Security Logs</h2>
      <p>All monitoring data can be securely synced to your private cloud account, so even if your device is lost or stolen, you don’t lose the evidence.</p>
      
      <h2>5. Stealth Mode for Ultimate Privacy</h2>
